          <span class="badge badge-danger" style="margin-bottom:4px">P0</span>
          <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px">调整价格带结构</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary)">降低0元课占比，提升高客单价课程曝光</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="badge badge-warning" style="margin-bottom:4px">P1</span>
          <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px">迭代广告素材</div>
